Museum Review: Hatshepsut and Her World
Author(s): Emily Teeter
Source: American Journal of Archaeology , Oct., 2006, Vol. 110, No. 4 (Oct., 2006), pp. 
649-653 
Published by: Archaeological Institute of America 
